Package: IonMobility
Type: Package
Title: Infrastructure for Ion Mobility enabled mass spectrometry
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2021-02-17
Authors@R: c(person("Crook", "Oliver M.",
		    email = "oliver.crook@stats.ox.ac.uk",
		    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5669-8506"),
		    role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: The IonMobility package extends the Spectra package to provide
    efficient storing and handling of of ion mobility enabled mass spectrometry
    data, as well as functionality for subsetting, processing and visualising
    such data. These comprises a self-contained functionality for all types of
    ion mobility mass spectrometry data. The package contains some basic
    computations.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1),
    S4Vectors,
    BiocParallel,
    ProtGenerics (>= 1.23.6),
    Spectra
